claims:
1. the diffusion breeding method for releasing of a harmonia axyridia control cigarette aphid, is characterized in that, step is as follows:
      (a) carry out the breeding of cigarette aphid in diffusion breeding canopy, diffusion is bred fly net (7) for canopy and is covered; Adopt floating method to cultivate the cigarette seedling, when the cigarette seedling has 5～6 true leaves, will be with the aphid tobacco leaf to be put on the cigarette seedling and make the breeding of cigarette aphid; Then the harmonia axyridia of field acquisition is female, male imago is put into fly net, after making harmonia axyridia take food the cigarette aphid, the mate and oviposit hatching develops into larva, perhaps directly collect low instar larvae, perhaps after larvae pupation, pupa is fetched under room temperature and sprouted wings, the adult of emergence is fed and is placed on the refrigerator cold-storage preservation with the cigarette aphid;
      (b) harmonia axyridia low instar larvae or adult are put into to low instar larvae transportation releasing device (9) or adult transportation releasing device (10), at field cigarette aphid initial stage of origination by the wooden dipper aphid of 1:100～120 than harmonia axyridia low instar larvae or adult are discharged into to field.
